  "detailed_description": "Step into the world of Mini Sports, an online game that offers a variety of 1vs1 mini-games. Challenge players from around the world or invite your friends to compete with you in classic and fun games like 8-ball pool, racing, badminton, curling, mini golf, and archery.<br><br><strong>🎱 8-Ball pool</strong><br>The classic pool game where players take turns to pot all their balls.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/5b4840d4784c86653e89a01a9106e609.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/5b4840d4784c86653e89a01a9106e609.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/5b4840d4784c86653e89a01a9106e609.mp4?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🏎️ Racing</strong><br>Compete in a race where the fastest to complete the laps wins. Use skillful driving to navigate the track and beat your opponent.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/ca5dc96060cb95b47856cda2439df7cc.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/ca5dc96060cb95b47856cda2439df7cc.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/ca5dc96060cb95b47856cda2439df7cc.mp4?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🏸 Badminton</strong><br>Basically tennis but with a shuttlecock instead of a ball. Get the shuttlecock to the opponent's side and win points.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/df46422c4d17b6c2e483bdeccd50d8ea.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/df46422c4d17b6c2e483bdeccd50d8ea.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/df46422c4d17b6c2e483bdeccd50d8ea.mp4?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🥌 Curling</strong><br>Take turns sliding stones on the ice and try to get your stone the closest to the center.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/052888ecc9e17358cdf13bb1514bd347.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/052888ecc9e17358cdf13bb1514bd347.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/052888ecc9e17358cdf13bb1514bd347.mp4?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>⛳ Mini Golf</strong><br>Get your golf ball through the obstacles and into the hole.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/99f3e6988ab20cfbe484e8a9aa12be5c.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/99f3e6988ab20cfbe484e8a9aa12be5c.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/99f3e6988ab20cfbe484e8a9aa12be5c.mp4?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🏹 Archery</strong><br>Shoot arrows at the target and try to hit as close to the center as you can.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/16ccbb23e3e62a155f818019d17b5104.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/16ccbb23e3e62a155f818019d17b5104.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/16ccbb23e3e62a155f818019d17b5104.mp4?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Are you ready prove your skills? Dive into Mini Sports now and let the games begin!",
  "about_the_game": "Step into the world of Mini Sports, an online game that offers a variety of 1vs1 mini-games. Challenge players from around the world or invite your friends to compete with you in classic and fun games like 8-ball pool, racing, badminton, curling, mini golf, and archery.<br><br><strong>🎱 8-Ball pool</strong><br>The classic pool game where players take turns to pot all their balls.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/5b4840d4784c86653e89a01a9106e609.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/5b4840d4784c86653e89a01a9106e609.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/5b4840d4784c86653e89a01a9106e609.mp4?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🏎️ Racing</strong><br>Compete in a race where the fastest to complete the laps wins. Use skillful driving to navigate the track and beat your opponent.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/ca5dc96060cb95b47856cda2439df7cc.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/ca5dc96060cb95b47856cda2439df7cc.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/ca5dc96060cb95b47856cda2439df7cc.mp4?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🏸 Badminton</strong><br>Basically tennis but with a shuttlecock instead of a ball. Get the shuttlecock to the opponent's side and win points.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/df46422c4d17b6c2e483bdeccd50d8ea.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/df46422c4d17b6c2e483bdeccd50d8ea.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/df46422c4d17b6c2e483bdeccd50d8ea.mp4?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🥌 Curling</strong><br>Take turns sliding stones on the ice and try to get your stone the closest to the center.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/052888ecc9e17358cdf13bb1514bd347.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/052888ecc9e17358cdf13bb1514bd347.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/052888ecc9e17358cdf13bb1514bd347.mp4?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>⛳ Mini Golf</strong><br>Get your golf ball through the obstacles and into the hole.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/99f3e6988ab20cfbe484e8a9aa12be5c.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/99f3e6988ab20cfbe484e8a9aa12be5c.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/99f3e6988ab20cfbe4